Property.name: ClinicalDocumentId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the clinical document id that this version is related to. </summary> <value> The clinical document id. </value>

Property.name: ClinicalDocumentVersionId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the clinical document version id. </summary> <value> The clinical document version id. </value>

Property.name: Package
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the package - This is the zipped clinical document and all it's attachements. </summary> <value> The package. </value>

Property.name: SourceSystemDocumentId

Property.name: SupersededDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date that this document was superseded. </summary> <value> The superseded date. </value>

Property.name: UploadedDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date/time the document was uploaded to the PCEHR. </summary> <value> The uploaded date. </value>
